325
00:18:37,870 --> 00:18:41,310
Oh, you want me to share credit?
喔 你要我同你分享荣誉?

326
00:18:41,820 --> 00:18:44,490
Get out!
出-去!

327
00:18:46,430 --> 00:18:48,730
Oh, bite me!
噢 别烦我!

328
00:18:50,580 --> 00:18:52,700
Sisters?
好姐妹?

329
00:18:55,940 --> 00:18:57,970
Excuse me, Dr. Cooper.
打扰一下 Cooper教授

330
00:18:57,990 --> 00:18:59,380
I'm Kathy O'Brien.
我是Kathy O'Brien

331
00:18:59,390 --> 00:19:03,190
I just finished reading your paper
reconciling the black hole information paradox
我刚拜读了你的那篇论文
有关解除黑洞信息悖论的

332
00:19:03,200 --> 00:19:07,870
with your theory of string
- network condensates, and it just took my breath away.
你用了基于弦网冷凝物的理论
真是令人惊叹啊 (让我都喘不过气了)

333
00:19:08,780 --> 00:19:11,960
Maybe when I publish it,
I'll include an inhaler.
也许等它发表的时候
我会考虑多加个喷雾器 (治哮喘的)

334
00:19:15,140 --> 00:19:19,000
Would you possibly have any
time for me to pick your brain?
你会不会正巧有空给我解释解释呢?

335
00:19:19,010 --> 00:19:20,270
Let's see. Today's Thursday.
让我想想 今天是星期四

336
00:19:20,280 --> 00:19:22,260
Thursday nights, I eat
pizza from Giacomo's.
星期四晚上 我吃Giacomo餐厅的匹萨

337
00:19:22,270 --> 00:19:24,240
Sausage, mushrooms, light olives.
要放香肠 蘑菇 还要一点橄榄油

338
00:19:24,250 --> 00:19:28,750
Great. I'll bring it to your
place. I have the address.
太好了 我会买去你家的 我有地址

339
00:19:31,230 --> 00:19:33,830
What a nice girl.
真是个好姑娘

340
00:19:34,690 --> 00:19:37,410
Sheldon, do you see
what just happened here?
Sheldon 你知道刚才怎么回事吗?

341
00:19:37,420 --> 00:19:40,760
Yes, I'm getting a free pizza.
当然 我有免费匹萨吃咯

342
00:19:42,660 --> 00:19:45,780
I'm on a roll.
我好运连连喔!

343
00:19:49,180 --> 00:19:51,040
More pad Thai, please.
再来点泰国菜

344
00:19:51,050 --> 00:19:53,230
Sheldon, you've already
had four servings.
Sheldon 你已经吃了四盒了

345
00:19:53,240 --> 00:19:55,700
You might want to
slow down a bit, buddy.
你该吃慢点 伙计 小心咽着

346
00:19:56,270 --> 00:19:59,160
Just one more bite.
就一小口

347
00:20:05,300 --> 00:20:06,930
Sheldon?
Sheldon?

348
00:20:07,320 --> 00:20:08,920
Sheldon, are you okay?
Sheldon 你还好吧?

349
00:20:08,930 --> 00:20:12,110
I'm just so... full.
我太... 饱了

350
00:20:23,260 --> 00:20:25,570
That's it. No more Thai food.
受不鸟了 再不吃泰国菜了

351
00:20:26,350 --> 00:20:30,510
翻译: 王泳东 gigigao 八重樱 饭特稀
校对: 欧屁屁

